(1, 1, '2015-11-21 19:59:26', '2015-11-21 19:59:26', 'Here is a really cool video that I think does a great job of explaining why someone would want to be a mentor to someone else.\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wtr--uo_WMc', 'Why Mentor?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2015-12-01 19:40:49', '2015-12-01 19:40:49', '', 0, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2015-11-21 19:59:26', '2015-11-21 19:59:26', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2015-11-22 00:24:36', '2015-11-22 00:24:36', '', 0, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2015-11-21 23:30:46', '2015-11-21 23:30:46', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #999999;">Give your mentoring program a boost in <strong>3 easy steps</strong>...</span></p>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-12" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/match.png" alt="Matching Mentors to Mentees" width="201" height="187" />\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Match.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Dream Extreme takes the guesswork (and the legwork) out of matching and makes more compatible, and therefore lasting, matches between mentors and mentees.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-13" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/manage.png" alt="manage" width="206" height="199" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Manage.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Track participation, mentor-mentee activities/feedback and match satisfaction in real-time through our proprietary tracking system. Peace out, spreadsheets!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/measure.png" alt="measure" width="209" height="202" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Measure.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Data. Data. Data. Our actionable intelligence and easy reporting will improve your program by helping you measure program outcomes...and secure that next grant!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-10 size-medium" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/640-300x225.png" alt="640" width="300" height="225" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">We get mentoring...and we think it''s awesome.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">That''s why we''re inventing an ''awesome-er'' way for you to do it.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We''ve taken an "eHarmony" approach to mentor matching, and combined it with actionable intelligence and innovative mobile technology. We''re the only solution available with our technology to help mentoring programs not only better manage day-to-day operations, but also better engage mentors and mentees.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">In addition, Dream ExtremeÂ is:</h3>\r\n<ul style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Scalable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Customizable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">White-labeled</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Affordable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We''re not just ''technology people.'' We''re mentors, too. We know how important your work is, and we''ve built Dream ExtremeÂ to help you stretch your dollars and get it done.</p>', 'How Dream Extreme works', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-dream-extreme-works', '', '', '2015-12-01 19:37:34', '2015-12-01 19:37:34', '', 0, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/?p=4', 0, 'post', '', 0),
