(186, 1, '2015-12-06 04:42:58', '2015-12-06 04:42:58', 'According to the study conducted by Arts University, Bournemouth, a third of people give up on their dream careers because they did not think they had the right skills. A mentor would be someone who managed to break into those careers or mastered an art and is therefore equipped to advise others on how to follow in their footsteps. As humans, we respond strongly to our fellow humans, and  creating the connection between mentor and mentee will result in real relationships that spark real change. Many historical advances arose out of joint efforts between people. The goal of this site is to empower people to follow their dreams by ensuring everyone has at least one other person they can turn to for encouragement and advice.\n\nDreamEX is aÂ website that features comprehensive guides for investigating routes to any career or hobby. AÂ trove of information would be made accessible to dreamers for every conceivable dream at varying levels of commitment from a free time hobby to a part-time gig to a full-time career path in the form of question and answer threads on a discussion board divided into general sections and specialized subsections, a platform for communication between dreamers and their mentors, links to financial resources, and single page at-a-glance summaries that detail the feasibility of a dream in particular contexts (location, skill set, budget range, etc).', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-06 04:42:58', '2015-12-06 04:42:58', '', 50, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/2015/12/06/50-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(187, 1, '2015-12-06 04:43:53', '2015-12-06 04:43:53', 'According to the study conducted by Arts University, Bournemouth, a third of people give up on their dream careers because they did not think they had the right skills. A mentor would be someone who managed to break into those careers or mastered an art and is therefore equipped to advise others on how to follow in their footsteps. As humans, we respond strongly to our fellow humans, and  creating the connection between mentor and mentee will result in real relationships that spark real change. Many historical advances arose out of joint efforts between people. The goal of this site is to empower people to follow their dreams by ensuring everyone has at least one other person they can turn to for encouragement and advice.\r\n\r\nDreamEX is aÂ website that features comprehensive guides for investigating routes to any career or hobby. AÂ trove of information would be made accessible to dreamers for every conceivable dream at varying levels of commitment from a free time hobby to a part-time gig to a full-time career path in the form of question and answer threads on a discussion board. The discussion board is divided into general sections and specialized subsections, becoming a platform for communication between dreamers and their mentors. We also supply links to financial resources, and single page at-a-glance summaries that detail the feasibility of a dream in particular contexts (location, skill set, budget range, etc).', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-06 04:43:53', '2015-12-06 04:43:53', '', 50, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/2015/12/06/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(188, 1, '2015-12-06 04:46:24', '2015-12-06 04:46:24', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #999999;">Give your mentoring program a boost in <strong>3 easy steps</strong>...</span></p>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-12" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/match.png" alt="Matching Mentors to Mentees" width="201" height="187" />\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Match.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Dream Extreme takes the guesswork (and the legwork) out of matching and createsÂ more compatible, and therefore lasting, matches between mentors and mentees.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-13" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/manage.png" alt="manage" width="206" height="199" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Manage.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Track participation and mentor-mentee activities, feedback, and match satisfaction in real-time through our proprietary tracking system. Peace out, spreadsheets!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/measure.png" alt="measure" width="209" height="202" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Measure.</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Data. Data. Data. Our actionable intelligence and easy reporting will improve your program by helping you measure program outcomes...and secure that next grant!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-10 size-medium" src="http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/640-300x225.png" alt="640" width="300" height="225" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">We get mentoring...and we think it''s awesome.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">That''s why we''re inventing an ''awesome-er'' way for you to do it.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We''ve taken an "eHarmony" approach to mentor matching, and combined it with actionable intelligence and innovative mobile technology. We''re the only solution available with our technology to help mentoring programs not only better manage day-to-day operations, but also better engage mentors and mentees.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">In addition, Dream ExtremeÂ is:</h3>\r\n<ul style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Scalable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Customizable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">White-labeled</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Affordable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We''re not just ''technology people.'' We''re mentors, too. We know how important your work is, and we''ve built Dream ExtremeÂ to help you stretch your dollars and get it done.</p>', 'How Mentoring works', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-06 04:46:24', '2015-12-06 04:46:24', '', 25, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/2015/12/06/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(189, 1, '2015-12-06 17:16:13', '2015-12-06 17:16:13', '\n\nThink about your career goals. What do you really want to do? Where do you want to be? \nLook for a person who is currently there and ask him/her to be your mentor. Ideally, this person is someone who has been in your shoes and can easily relate to your current situation.\n\n[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bvAEJ8G9l9U[/embed]\n&nbsp;', 'Mentee Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '57-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-06 17:16:13', '2015-12-06 17:16:13', '', 57, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/2015/12/06/57-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
